        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Sun River Hydropower Authorization Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Bureau of Reclamation to construct, operate, and maintain facilities (e.g., dams) in the Sun River project in Montana for hydroelectric power generation.</p>]]>
